      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 93,
      "message": "I thought about that.\n\nI also thought about another possible change, which is to not abort if an entry is missing -- perhaps you had entries #1 and #3, and wanted to comment out #2 and have it skip to #3.\n\nIf you make both of these changes, you have an infinite loop. For this reason, I thought it best to have some limit.",
