      "line": 93,
      "message": "Hi Pamela, I initially had this statement include \"repository1\". However, this first repository is listed in the properties files without any numeric identifier as \"repository\". Instead, I added \"first\" to help clarify this. The remaining repositories use the numeric indicator. \"repository2,repository3, .... repository9\". I can work on a better solution to help identify which repo is which.",
